				<wikidot:authorName>Uncle Nicolini</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3487700</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I would like to thank my dear friends <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541282788" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2893766&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541282788" alt="Croquembouche" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2893766)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/croquembouche" >Croquembouche</a></span> for critiquing this piece AND creating the End of Death canon, which is an absolute blast to write in.</p> <p>Speaking of blasts and writing, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1541282788" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span> is an absolute bro and I love writing with him. We hope you like these tales as much as we like writing them.</p> <p>The image used is <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Offices_in_the_1990s#/media/File:USL_office_in_Summit_with_room_number.jpg">C.C 4.0</a></p> <p>So my friends, I ask of you; <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=emGh_5E3idQ">Who wants to live forever?</a></p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
